name: Exercise Daily
description: Engage in at least 30 minutes of physical activity every day.

name: Drink 8 Glasses of Water
description: Stay hydrated by drinking at least 8 glasses of water daily.

name: Read Before Bed
description: Develop a habit of reading for 30 minutes before going to bed.

name: Meditate
description: Practice mindfulness meditation for 10 minutes each morning.

name: Limit Screen Time
description: Reduce screen time to less than 1 hour per day.
